text:
GUYS...PLEASE SUPPORT NCT2020
-THEY WERE REALLY EXCITED, HAPPY AND WORKED HARD.
-THEY GIVE US FREE CONTENTS EVEN WHEN THEY DON'T HAVE CBS.
- EACH SUB UNIT DESERVE THE LOVE , SUPPORT AND RECOGNITION.
Through NCT 2020, we all benefit, make your efforts count. Do it for your bias who worked hard. Do it for the sub unit you love so much. Do it for their joy. Do it for the pride of your favorite group. We need positive energy until the cb ends. Don't assume things without looking at the whole situation. Don't ruin this cb. SM is promoting and focuses a lot on NCT. Also thanks to the marketing strategy. SM can make boys nominated and win in musical shows. Kick It Era? don't u remember? the day when we won for sales? The same story can happen but WE MUST TO WORK HARD WITH OUR WEAKNESS. DIGITALS AND STREAMING. VLIVE = 12M with 2B hearts. Imagine if we manage to keep the joy and encourage others to vote or stream? Our power is greater not to stop fighting for the boys. They deserve it. ONE for all, ALL for one. 
Other fandoms would like to have the amount of content we have. Let's not lose the opportunity to also be seen as the "lazy fandom", other fandoms are afraid of our power, they analyzed our weakness. Let's cheer up, buy, vote or let's all stream, other fandoms underestimate us but we will show true power when we are ALL together. Fighting
